    },
    {
      "text": "The exclaves of Madha and Musandam are surrounded by the United Arab Emirates on their land borders, while Musandam's coastal boundaries are formed by the Strait of Hormuz and the Gulf of Oman.",
      "source_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oman",
